videos.description: Rutgers WR Janarion Grant is carted off the field after nearly scoring from 76 yards out.

videos.headline: Iowa strikes first against Rutgers
videos.description: Iowa QB C.J. Beathard finds George Kittle for the 36-yard touchdown to put the Hawkeyes up 7-0 on Rutgers.

videos.headline: Rutgers evens the score with Iowa
videos.description: Rutgers QB Chris Laviano finds Andre Patton for the 14 yard touchdown to tie the game with Iowa at 7.

videos.headline: Iowa takes 14-7 lead on 26-yard TD run
videos.description: Iowa RB Akrum Wadley weaves his way through the Rutgers defense for a 26-yard touchdown run to give the Hawkeyes a 14-7 lead.
